  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/31feb3a9f959546da6399fbf67a6c361.webp?t=1728405700\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br>The Octopus Princess has been kidnapped by the evil celebrity chef, Shefu and plans to cook her on live TV for the entire world to see! As loyal samurai from her kingdom, embark on a perilous quest to Restaurant Island as Tako and Sakana to try and save her from this culinary calamity! The Island itself is full of dangerous food themed dungeons each guarded by Shefu's evil and corrupted cooking. It will take everything Tako and Sakana have in them to brave through the eight levels to save their princess.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/c6be75c40a610394cbd65f5498b43f7f.poster.avif?t=1728405700\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/c6be75c40a610394cbd65f5498b43f7f.webm?t=1728405700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/c6be75c40a610394cbd65f5498b43f7f.mp4?t=1728405700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/f4f12c70fb7466f4817d4707bf0087c1.webp?t=1728405700\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br>Point and click your way through Shefu's army of dangerous delectables!  Takoyaki Surprise blends fast-paced action with a zany vibe that will give you more than your fill of excitement.You'll feel like you've been transported to a colorful world where the stakes are stacked higher than the plates and there's never any room for dessert!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/4c1cfbf0627d5aa471890c0c00f23f92.poster.avif?t=1728405700\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/4c1cfbf0627d5aa471890c0c00f23f92.webm?t=1728405700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/4c1cfbf0627d5aa471890c0c00f23f92.mp4?t=1728405700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475510/extras/e4d3b862d8f1e63850464640f7f8a6db.webp?t=1728405700\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beautiful full-color pixel art graphics<br></li><li>Two modes of play<br></li><li>Epic soundtrack with loads of international vibes<br></li><li>Eight intense stages<br></li><li>Exploding food<br></li><li>So... many... food puns<br></li><li>And much more!</li></ul>",
